NAME
		bcon - HEX/BIN/DEC Converter

SYNTAX
		bcon [hex/bin/dec] (Numbers to convert) [,output]
		
DESCRIPTION
		A Base converter which can be used to convert between Hexadecimal, Binary and Decimal.
		First argument should contain the common name for the base unless the number starts with a prefix
		E.g 0x = Hex, 0b = Binary, Nothing = Decimal
		The command will return a conversion list of all the Bases.